page.title: 20TRADE BILLINGSHURST
page.content: A SMALL SHOPPING PRECINCT (JENGERS MEAD) IS SITUATED IN THE MIDDLE OF THE VILLAGE.HERE WE HAVE A SUPERMARKET, BUTCHER,BAKER,FREEZER SHOP,LADIES AND CHILDRENS FASHIONS, A DO-IT-YOURSELF/HARDWARE SHOP,HI-FI, GREENGROCER,DRY CLEANERS,LAUNDERETTE, WINE SHOP,DRUG STORE,FISH AND CHIP SHOP,SPORTS EQUIPMENT,TRAVEL AGENT AND A CHINESE RESTAURANT.IN THE HIGH STREET IS A WOOL/FABRIC SHOP,CHEMIST, CHINAWARE SHOP,NEWSAGENT,WINE SHOP, INDIAN RESTAURANT,BOOK SHOP,ARTS AND CRAFTS,GREENGROCER,FLORIST,TELEVISION, AND LADIES FASHIONS. ON THE OUTSKIRTS OF BILLINGSHURST ARE 2 SMALL SUPERMARKETS,AN EGG FARM,DAIRY, GARDEN FURNITURE AND A FARM PRODUCE SHOP.
